iv></div><h3 class=\"relative text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display mb-4 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors duration-300\">Progressive Web Apps</h3><p class=\"relative text-text-secondary mb-8 leading-relaxed font-light\">Native-quality experiences that run everywhere. Offline support, push notifications, and app store distribution.</p><div class=\"relative flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">Service Workers</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">Capacitor</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">TWA</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">iOS</span></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-16 h-16 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" class=\"w-full h-full\"><path d=\"M0 100 L100 100 L100 0 Z\" fill=\"url(#corner-gradient)\"></path><defs><linearGradient id=\"corner-gradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\"><stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"var(--brand)\" stop-opacity=\"0\"></stop><stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"var(--brand)\" stop-opacity=\"0.2\"></stop></linearGradient></defs></svg></div></div><div class=\"group relative bg-surface border border-border p-8 md:p-12 overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand/0 via-brand/0 to-brand/0 group-hover:from-brand/[0.02] group-hover:via-brand/[0.05] group-hover:to-brand/[0.02] transition-all duration-500\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-brand to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-brand to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-px h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-brand to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-px h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-brand to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"relative mb-8\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 border border-border flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-brand transition-colors duration-300\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-2xl text-text-secondary group-hover:text-brand transition-colors\">auto_awesome</span></div></div><h3 class=\"relative text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display mb-4 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors duration-300\">Process Automation</h3><p class=\"relative text-text-secondary mb-8 leading-relaxed font-light\">Replace manual workflows with intelligent systems. API integrations, data pipelines, and workflow orchestration.</p><div class=\"relative flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">Python</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">n8n</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">Custom APIs</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">Webhooks</span></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-16 h-16 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" class=\"w-full h-full\"><path d=\"M0 100 L100 100 L100 0 Z\" fill=\"url(#corner-gradient)\"></path><defs><linearGradient id=\"corner-gradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\"><stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"var(--brand)\" stop-opacity=\"0\"></stop><stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"var(--brand)\" stop-opacity=\"0.2\"></stop></linearGradient></defs></svg></div></div><div class=\"group relative bg-surface border border-border p-8 md:p-12 overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand/0 via-brand/0 to-brand/0 group-hover:from-brand/[0.02] group-hover:via-brand/[0.05] group-hover:to-brand/[0.02] transition-all duration-500\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-brand to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-brand to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-px h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-brand to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-px h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-brand to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"relative mb-8\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 border border-border flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-brand transition-colors duration-300\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-2xl text-text-secondary group-hover:text-brand transition-colors\">psychology</span></div></div><h3 class=\"relative text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display mb-4 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors duration-300\">AI Integration</h3><p class=\"relative text-text-secondary mb-8 leading-relaxed font-light\">Practical machine learning and LLM integration. Chat interfaces, document processing, and predictive features.</p><div class=\"relative flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">OpenAI</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">LangChain</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">Embeddings</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-alt text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border group-hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors duration-300\">RAG</span></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-16 h-16 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" class=\"w-full h-full\"><path d=\"M0 100 L100 100 L100 0 Z\" fill=\"url(#corner-gradient)\"></path><defs><linearGradient id=\"corner-gradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\"><stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"var(--brand)\" stop-opacity=\"0\"></stop><stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"var(--brand)\" stop-opacity=\"0.2\"></stop></linearGradient></defs></svg></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"work\" class=\"section\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-16 lg:mb-24\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><div class=\"brand-line\"></div><span class=\"section-label\">Selected Work</span></div><div class=\"space-y-24 lg:space-y-32\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] bg-surface overflow-hidden \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=1200&amp;q=80\" alt=\"FinTech Dashboard\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display mb-6\" style=\"opacity:0\">FinTech Dashboard</h3><p class=\"text-text-secondary text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed font-light\" style=\"opacity:0\">Real-time trading platform with sub-millisecond data updates and complex charting.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\" style=\"opacity:0\"><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-surface text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border\">React</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-surface text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border\">WebSockets</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-surface text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border\">D3.js</span></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] bg-surface overflow-hidden lg:order-2\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556742049-0cfed4f6a45d?w=1200&amp;q=80\" alt=\"E-commerce Platform\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><div class=\"lg:order-1\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display mb-6\" style=\"opacity:0\">E-commerce Platform</h3><p class=\"text-text-secondary text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed font-light\" style=\"opacity:0\">Headless commerce solution handling 100k+ daily orders with custom inventory management.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\" style=\"opacity:0\"><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-surface text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border\">Next.js</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-surface text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border\">Stripe</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-surface text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border\">PostgreSQL</span></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/3] bg-surface overflow-hidden \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160550-217358c7db81?w=1200&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Healthcare Portal\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display mb-6\" style=\"opacity:0\">Healthcare Portal</h3><p class=\"text-text-secondary text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed font-light\" style=\"opacity:0\">HIPAA-compliant patient portal with telemedicine integration and automated scheduling.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\" style=\"opacity:0\"><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-surface text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border\">React</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-surface text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border\">Node.js</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-surface text-xs font-mono text-text-muted border border-border\">WebRTC</span></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"about\" class=\"section bg-surface-alt relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] opacity-5 pointer-events-none\"><div class=\"w-full h-full border border-brand rounded-full\"></div></div><div class=\"container relative z-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-40px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"brand-line\"></div><span class=\"section-label\">About H2</span></div><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display mb-10\">We&#x27;re a different kind of<!-- --> <span class=\"text-text-secondary\">development</span> <span class=\"gradient-text\">partner.</span></h2><div class=\"space-y-6 text-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed font-light\"><p style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Most agencies sell hours. We sell outcomes. Every project starts with understanding your business goals, then we build the technology to get you there.</p><p style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Our team spans full-stack engineering, DevOps, and AI integration. We&#x27;ve shipped everything from MVPs to enterprise platforms handling millions in transactions.</p><p style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">When you work with H2, you get direct access to senior engineers who care about your success. No account managers, no junior devs learning on your dime.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-6\"><div class=\"border-t border-border pt-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(20px)\"><div class=\"text-xl font-display mb-1\"><span class=\"gradient-text\">Full-Stack</span></div><div class=\"text-text-secondary font-light text-sm\">End-to-end development</div></div><div class=\"border-t border-border pt-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(20px)\"><div class=\"text-xl font-display mb-1\"><span class=\"gradient-text\">Automation</span></div><div class=\"text-text-secondary font-light text-sm\">Workflow optimization</div></div><div class=\"border-t border-border pt-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(20px)\"><div class=\"text-xl font-display mb-1\"><span class=\"gradient-text\">AI/ML</span></div><div class=\"text-text-secondary font-light text-sm\">Intelligent systems</div></div><div class=\"border-t border-border pt-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(20px)\"><div class=\"text-xl font-display mb-1\"><span class=\"gradient-text\">Cloud</span></div><div class=\"text-text-secondary font-light text-sm\">Scalable infrastructure</div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"contact\" class=\"section relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[800px] h-[800px] opacity-5 pointer-events-none\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 border border-brand rounded-full animate-[spin_60s_linear_infinite]\"></div></div><div class=\"container relative z-10\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><div class=\"brand-line\"></div><span class=\"section-label\">Contact</span></div><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Let&#x27;s build something<!-- --> <span class=\"gradient-text\">great.</span></h2><p class=\"text-text-secondary text-lg mb-12 leading-relaxed font-light\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Tell us about your project. We&#x27;ll respond within 24 hours with next steps and how we can help.</p><form class=\"space-y-6\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><label class=\"block font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-text-secondary mb-3\">Name</label><input type=\"text\" required=\"\" class=\"input\" placeholder=\"John Doe\" value=\"\"/></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><label class=\"block font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-text-secondary mb-3\">Email</label><input type=\"email\" required=\"\" class=\"input\" placeholder=\"john@company.com\" value=\"\"/></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><label class=\"block font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-text-secondary mb-3\">Company</label><input type=\"text\" class=\"input\" placeholder=\"Acme Inc.\" value=\"\"/></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><label class=\"block font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-text-secondary mb-3\">Message</label><textarea required=\"\" rows=\"5\" class=\"input resize-none\" placeholder=\"Tell us about your project...\"></textarea></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Send message</button></form></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-surface border-t border-border py-12\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><img src=\"/h2-logo.png\" alt=\"H2 Logo\" class=\"w-10 h-10\"/><span class=\"font-display font-semibold text-lg\">H2</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-mono text-text-secondary\"><a href=\"#work\" class=\"h